item.title: CVE-2020-4975|2024-08-04T08:14:59.260Z -- ibm -- rational%20team%20concert
item.description: IBM Engineering products are vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 192435.
